+
+- Zustand store in `connectionStore.ts`: CONNECTED â†’ GRACE_PERIOD (2s) â†’ RECONNECTING (30s total) â†’ DISCONNECTED
+- `onDisconnected` guard checks `current !== "connected"` â€” must allow re-entry from `disconnected`
+  to handle Retry button flow (forceReconnect fires notifyConnectionChange(false) before new socket opens)
