+- WS error messages that trigger `emitSendAttemptFailed`: both `"not connected"` AND `"disconnected"`
+  must be matched â€” `"WebSocket disconnected"` (from onclose pending-command rejection) will be missed
+  if only checking `"not connected"`
+- `platform/ws â†’ connectionStore` is safe (no circular import). `session.queries â†’ connectionEvents` is safe.
+- `ConnectionBanner` animates `height` (violates project guidelines) â€” causes panel jitter on 32â†’44 change
+- `ConnectionOrb` color crossfade: CSS `transition-colors` on a class swap is better than Framer Motion
+  `backgroundColor` interpolation (avoids paint-per-frame)
